title.narrative: Provincial Reconstruction Team Support: Programme and Operations

description.narrative: This activity (Provincial Reconstruction Team Support: Programme and Operations) is a component of Helmand PRT Operations Support Project reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £118,424. This component benefits Afghanistan, and works in the following sector(s): Decentralisation and support to subnational government, Democratic participation and civil society, Civilian peace-building, conflict prevention and resolution. The start date is 15-04-2011 and the end date is 30-11-2012.
